            impedit laudantium facilis quam blanditiis!
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <h1 class="text-7xl text-blue-100 font-medium w-full mt-36 mb-36">
        Envíos
      </h1>
      <section class="flex flex-wrap justify-between items-center w-full">
        <div class="flex justify-start items-start flex-col p-20 w-3/6 p-">
          <h2 class="text-4xl text-brown-500 font-medium w-full">
            Realizamos envíos a toda Nicaragua
          </h2>
